---
title: Nasu Dengaku Style Miso and Honey Glazed Aubergine with Udon Noodles, Stir-Fried Veg and Peanuts
description: Nasu dengaku is a classic Japanese side dish made with aubergine sliced in half, scored and brushed with a sweet and savory miso sauce. Our version places your nasu dengaku inspired aubergine on top of thick udon noodles and miso veg for a hearty vegetarian dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R48_W45_UK_HVV27141-3_Main_low-a9414c6b.jpg
